title: Pikelan Day #2
body:
This week: 

To impress Pike, Scanlan spends about a month learning everything he can about how to make fancy cocktails. And I mean with the tricks and the flair and perfect taste and everything. When he’s finally content with his own skills, he puts on a real show at a party of one of their friends. He pretends he’s looking for ‘the best cocktail’, so he makes it a game where he makes a bunch of cocktails and everyone has to vote on their favourite. Pike is delighted. She loves to be entertained and she applauds him as loudly as she can and has a sip of everything he makes. Her vote ends up being the deciding one and Scanlan spends the entire evening making mental notes of what tastes she likes and beaming because of the smile he’s able to put on her face.

(At the end of the night, Pike whispers to Grog that she really prefers whiskey. But whatever. Scanlan was happy, and that’s what counts, right?)
